OL,7,FRealising he was about to find himself
OL,8,Fhomeless, Muhammet Kaya began
OL,9,Fformulating a plan in case he found
OL,10,Fhimself without a roof over his head `
OL,11,Fbut the best the 19-year-old could come
OL,12,Fup with was the idea of sleeping in his
OL,13,Fcar.
OL,15,F"I had bought myself a car for #280 and
OL,16,Fhad seriously considered putting the
OL,17,Fseats down, putting some stuff down in
OL,18,Fthe back and sleeping in there,"
OL,19,FMuhammet tells i. "If I couldn't have
OL,20,Fsorted anything else out, this is what
OL,21,FI was looking at doing."
OL,3,CChristmas appeal: 'I was on the verge
OL,4,Cof homelessness and about to sleep in
OL,5,Cmy car'
